' @id(USE-VIEW-DIAGRAMS)
' @id(USE-FISHEYE-FOCUS)
' @id(USE-TOGGLE-PANELS)
' @id(USE-VIEW-OCL)
' @id(USE-VIEW-DEPLOY)  <<added>> this cycle (0010)
' Cycle 0010 diff (current side): one element added, none removed.
title mdd view — diagram viewer · cycle 0010 diff (current)

left to right direction

actor "Developer" as Dev

rectangle "mdd-viewer" {
  usecase "View rendered diagram\n(shapes AND text legible)" as View
  usecase "Browse model files" as Browse
  usecase "Pan and zoom canvas\n(scroll zoom, drag pan)" as PanZoom
  usecase "Focus via center fisheye" as Fisheye
  usecase "Collapse / expand side panels" as Panels
  usecase "Inspect model IDs and trace links" as Trace
  usecase "View OCL constraints\n(source or diagram)" as ViewOcl
  usecase "View deployment diagrams\n(dedicated DEPLOY section,\nNOT parity-gated)" as ViewDeploy <<added>>
}

Dev --> View
Dev --> Browse
Dev --> PanZoom
Dev --> Fisheye
Dev --> Panels
Dev --> Trace
Dev --> ViewOcl
Dev --> ViewDeploy

View ..> Browse : <<include>>
View ..> PanZoom : <<extend>>
View ..> Fisheye : <<extend>>
View ..> Panels : <<extend>>
ViewOcl ..> PanZoom : <<extend>>
ViewDeploy ..> PanZoom : <<extend>>

note bottom of ViewDeploy
  ADDED in cycle 0010 (USE-VIEW-DEPLOY): the rail gains
  a third source (project.deploy_files()) rendered as a
  dedicated DEPLOY section, OUTSIDE the parity gate.
  Realized by SEQ-VIEW-DEPLOY.
end note
@enduml
